Based on practical examples, the subject provides an overview of how the clinical pharmacist can contribute to the work of the clinical nutrition therapy team. Students solve a sample task as homework. In the webinar, there will be a discussion based on a sample task.Objectives/eesmärkid:  The purpose of the subject is to provide an overview of the principles of clinical feeding, to introduce the principles of enteral and parenteral operation, and to provide an overview of the role of the clinical pharmacist in the feeding treatment team.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  A student who has passed the subject: * knows the main principles of clinical nutrition
